title: One Born Every Minute
overview: One Born Every Minute is a gripping fly-on-a-wall series that takes a tender and intimate look at the hustle and bustle of the Birth Unit inside Sydney's Westmead Hospital, following the journey of expectant mothers, their families and the midwives.From the reception desk to the operating theatre, each of the glorious and unpredictable moments of child birth are captured via 60 remote operated cameras that record 24/7, ensuring nothing about the experience is missed.
